Usage:

FoxitReader [-Register] | [-NoRegister] |

 [<PDF filename> [-ps <Password>] [-n <Page Number>] [-ImportFDF <FDF filename>] ] |

 [/p <PDF filename> [-ps <Password>] ] |

 [/t <PDF filename> <Printer> [-ps <Password>] ]
-Register Set Foxit Reader as default reader.\n
-NoRegister Open Foxit Reader but won't set it as default reader.\n
-n <Page Number> Specify most recently read page number.\n
-ImportFDF <FDF filename> Import the form data from the specified FDF file.\n
/p <PDF filename> Print this file with default printer.\n
/t <PDF filename> <Printer> Print this file with specific printer.\n
